{"tid":657493,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"唔知點面對佢地兩父子好 老公係咁打黎 好似好擔心咁","createTime":"2018-05-08T07:08:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-08T10:46:27.000Z","uid":14719,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a975cc6e1e0244f2630b72f42326d399f619dcb2","tid":657493,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T07:08:17.000Z","msg":"我老公同佢前妻都離左婚幾年<br />\n直到個仔都就快成年所以今年先同佢結婚<br />\n雖然佢大我十年<br />\n我又知道佢有個仔<br />\n但係我真係唔係為左錢定係乜野<br />\n我係真心鐘意佢<br />\n<br />\n老公有啲毒撚性格 小小戇直,加上屋企有第3個人<br />\n所以成日都唔夠膽搞我<br />\n怎至我懷疑佢可能不舉<br />\n但我又唔好意思開聲...<br />\n結左婚成年都未搞過...<br />\n有需求都好正常既..<br />\n<br />\n所以我都習慣左自慰...但係...<br />\n<br />\n有日老公返工之後<br />\n我就自慰<br />\n點知比個仔撞見到<br />\n<br />\n本身都打算扮無野<br />\n點知去佢房 見到佢居然開始打J...<br />\n就係咁就順勢...<br />\n<br />\n依家唔知點面對佢地兩父子好<br />\n走左出去到到依家我都未返屋企,<br />\n我老公係咁打黎,好似好擔心咁"},{"pid":"4555655d2b5f785a1c5ba0347f77bba9049aa924","tid":657493,"uid":94009,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T07:09:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/08/150942_d85aa92b060c6c3de349f08e5eb1dcc3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F08%2F150942_d85aa92b060c6c3de349f08e5eb1dcc3.jpg&h=8c0dffbf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"43aeff375e16e7583cdecb8bb488753acd529774","tid":657493,"uid":174766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T07:11:00.000Z","msg":"一家三個基?"},{"pid":"cd3c84c796d93edcbb1852b83a397c9fa038287d","tid":657493,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T07:11:23.000Z","msg":"樓主加油"},{"pid":"9608c5ac7ad2218d9b4ae5d9c76857c6cd6cab46","tid":657493,"uid":92611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T07:11:26.000Z","msg":"GAY POST?"},{"pid":"f310cb3efcd6358432d892f27fd72e02666f2d7a","tid":657493,"uid":44277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T07:13:31.000Z","msg":"Show Blocked User - 巴